Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:25.24,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yami Sukehiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:28.15,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,As the captain who leads \Nthe rest of the Black Bulls,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.15,0:22:31.08,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,he does most of his thinking on the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:34.54,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Our investigative team \Nasked him one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:39.56,sign_32477_350_Why_the_toilet__,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1787)}Why the toilet...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:44.05,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Why else? It's because the toilet is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:46.09,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But let me just say one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:48.94,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Before going in, you need to \Nmake sure there's toilet paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.94,0:22:51.30,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Those who enter a bathroom\N without toilet paper
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:54.01,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,are like birds who've had\N their wings torn off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:22:56.12,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,They'll never be able to \Nfly out to the blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:22:58.81,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,that lies beyond the bathroom ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:04.39,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, the one in charge of the toilet\Npaper here is the brat, but he always forgets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.39,0:23:10.31,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen hell many times because of him, \Nbut I showed him an even worse hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.37,0:23:10.31,italicstop,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami! I'm going to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.06,0:23:14.88,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,After that, his remarks about the \Ntoilet continued for hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:20.83,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But there was one thing we wanted to ask \Nhim before we finished this interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:25.86,sign_33587_363_How_long_are_you,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1791)}How long are you going to stay on the toilet...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:27.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey! Captain Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:29.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to stay in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.74,0:23:32.84,top,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I can't come out because \Nyou didn't restock the toilet paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:36.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out of here, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.43,0:23:44.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... I can't just fool around \Nafter you guys worked so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.77,0:23:49.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 50: \N"End of the Battle, End of Despair."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 50\N\N{\fs18}End of the Battle, End of Despair
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.53,0:23:53.70,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Mister Despair.\NThat's important, so I said it twice!
